# Config file for the SN module

D stratifySN   runtime control for turning the stratification of SN on or off,
D if off SN are distributed evenly throughout the domain
D also turns of uv stratification
PARAMETER stratifyHeat    BOOLEAN FALSE
PARAMETER useHeat	  BOOLEAN TRUE
PARAMETER coolOff	  BOOLEAN FALSE
PARAMETER coolTime	  BOOLEAN FALSE

#should not be here
D   hgas            Scale height of the gas distribution

#actual used stuff 
D   theatmax        maximum temperature above which there is no stationary heating
D   h_uv      	    UV field stratification

D Stuff for CR ionization and heating of gas. - JW
D Switch for CRs.
PARAMETER use_cr_heating BOOLEAN FALSE
D crIonRate		the background CR ionization rate
D Note that the CR heating rate is calculated from this assuming 20 eV
D CRs. The default is 6.8x10^-16 from M02 as listed in Padovani et al 2009 
D for protons (see table 4.) - JW
PARAMETER crIonRate	REAL 6.8E-16
D crIonNH
D crIonExp		These two values are by default 1 such that you
D &			get a uniform CR heating and ionization from the
D &			background, but you can set them to use eqn 27 from
D &			Padovani et al 2009 using for example M02 from table 4
D &			and setting NH = 1e20.
PARAMETER crIonNH       REAL 1.0E0
PARAMETER crIonExp      REAL 1.0E0
D crIonEnergy		Average CR ionization energy in eV(default is 20 eV)
PARAMETER crIonEnergy	REAL 20.0E0
D Background UV field strength in Habing units.
PARAMETER Gzero         REAL 1.69

D dust_sputter_temp At temperatures above this value dust
D &                 heating AND cooling will be switched off.
D &                 Default value 3e5 due to Fig. 25.4 of Draine's book.
D &                 At temperatures theatmax < T < dust_sputter_temp,
D &                 dust heating will turn off, but dust cooling will continue
D &                 to operate.

PARAMETER dust_sputter_temp REAL 3.0E5

D he_pe_recipe   Select recipe for photoelectric heating efficiency.
D &              WD01 = Weingartner/Draine 2001.
D &              BT94 = Bakes/Tielens 1994 as implemented in Wolfire+ 2003.
D &              NOGF = no G-factor, simple knob following Joung/M-MML 2006
D &              and Hill+ (incl JCIM, M-MML) 2018.
PARAMETER he_pe_recipe STRING "WD01" ["WD01", "BT94", "NOGF"]

D he_pe_norm    Total photoelectric heating rate (erg/s) for both gas and dust.
D &             Default from Wolfire+ 2003, slight edit of Bakes/Tielens 1994.
PARAMETER he_pe_norm REAL   1.3E-24

PARAMETER theatmax	REAL 1.0E7
PARAMETER theatmin	REAL 1.0E0

PARAMETER subfactor	REAL 0.1d0 
PARAMETER maxcycles	INTEGER 5000 

#radiation stuff
PARAMETER tradmin	REAL 4.7967E12
PARAMETER tradmax	REAL 4.7967E12
PARAMETER dradmin	REAL 4.7967E12
PARAMETER dradmax	REAL 4.7967E12
PARAMETER h_uv		REAL 0.3

#radiation stuff
PARAMETER absTmin	REAL 10.
PARAMETER absTmax	REAL 1e9
PARAMETER dtThres	REAL -0.01

#heating rate
VARIABLE phhe

PARAMETER he_abundM REAL  0.1
PARAMETER he_metal REAL 4.


